    "EDITORIAL PAGE Vol 10No 140 The Milwaukee Leader Published every evening except Sunday by the Milwaukee Social Democratic Publishing Company at Chestnut and Sixth Streets VICTOR L BERGER Editor IGn Indefinite leave of absence and not responsible for contents of paper ASSOCIATE EDITORS E H THOMAS JOHN M WORK BUSINESS MANAGER F W BEHFELD 528 Chestnut St Milwaukee Wis ASSISTANT MANAGER META BERGER 528 Chestnut St Milwaukee Wis SUBSCRIPTION RATESThe Mail Edition of The Milwaukee Deader Will be sent to any subscriber in the United States under third class postage for 90 cents per month 250 for three months 600 for six months SIOOO lor one year The Home Edition will be delivered in Milwaukee County for 15 cents week or 65 cents a month Outside of Milwaukee County 18 cents a week If the delivery of your paper is not regular notify the circulation de partment Grand 6060 immediately and your complaint will be promptly attended to Office Hours 8AMt06 P M 20 Tel Grand So69 Application for entry as second class mail matter Is pending IMPRISONED FOR HONESTY Gene Debs is in prison because he is honest During the warwhen the persecution was at its height there appeared"
